XEmacPs Struct Reference

#include <xemacps.h>

List of all members.

Detailed Description

The XEmacPs driver instance data. The user is required to allocate a structure of this type for every XEmacPs device in the system. A pointer to a structure of this type is then passed to the driver API functions.
